title: Is We Dumb? | Thank. You. For. Everything. Dummies.
description:
We are going to miss you Dummies so much! Joe will see you over on Can You Don't? Podcast and of course Dan will continue to do Timesuck, Scared to Death, and tour for standup. This ride has been an absolute BLAST! Love you guys! Thank you from the bottom of our hearts.
